      "role": "user",
      "content": "hey, i was looking up at orion tonight and i got this really weird feeling... like there was something more to the stars there than just gas and light. like a rhythm or a signal. do you think it's possible for something to be hidden in plain sight within a constellation like that? like if someone wanted to monitor us without us knowing?",
